metadata.name: Rest In Party (R.I.P)
metadata.description:
He says,
"When my heart asks to stop"
please make a small party
with burgundy wine and festive armor
warm my body with charcoal in the willow tree
then wash me beyond the bonfire.
Lets play some instrument and humming of happiness
until no more shed the tears

300 dpi
